{"tid":689952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港省] 用順豐嘅人，做人做狗自己簡。","createTime":"2018-06-04T12:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T21:57:42.000Z","uid":135160,"like":88,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5430d51972feaad1343f7f0dc7b5bafbdfa59d","tid":689952,"uid":135160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟平日都唔會用順豐。最近有野寄比朋友（本地），去到見佢轉左無用手寫單，已經心知不妙。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母用電子單掃乜撚qr code，個職員叫我down wechat，我心諗佢都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我用其他app掃佢個閪碼啦，首先你要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">企係個courter 等</span>80秒佢sd比你嘅驗證碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後要係電話填地址 收件人 電話 。<br />\n咁我咪退出去whatsapp copy個fd地址 點知一㩒番入去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢個界面就消失左</span>，我個時趕時間就燥燥地就話拎著單番屋企自己搞撚完先比佢寄。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁番撚到去，都好正常入左張單嘅資料，然後我禁查詢訂單，屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/203359_76310a6aef6d1f541bc3d48d09711816.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F203359_76310a6aef6d1f541bc3d48d09711816.png&h=b2d9b4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜撚野香港省，睇撚到我眼都突，即刻取消訂單，同個fd講寄比佢算數，真係痴撚線公司嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用開順豐個d人，做人做狗自己簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順豐幾乎已經係香港市場獨大，你班人繼續用真係不堪設想。"},{"pid":"d0a5081861d3f0a0d4aeb48650ffda0ea77bc6a0","tid":689952,"uid":173397,"like":12,"dislike":38,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fc22d1a7207e07db6a47d14ae513b2ff9722804","tid":689952,"uid":21423,"like":43,"dislike":7,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e289323b449b083b9a9645ec8a34f1817566313","tid":689952,"uid":165360,"like":8,"dislike":23,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53f8f69d57f9deb